01:10:43,240 --> 01:10:46,960
You'll throw boss a reach-around,
show him you're a good bitch.

727
01:10:47,120 --> 01:10:49,400
I'm nobody's little bitch!

728
01:10:49,560 --> 01:10:50,880
You fuckin' hear me?

729
01:10:51,040 --> 01:10:54,080
- He'll pay me what I tell him to pay!
- That's enough!

730
01:10:54,560 --> 01:10:55,720
Sit down!

731
01:11:00,360 --> 01:11:03,120
It's been a long fucking day.

732
01:11:03,280 --> 01:11:06,920
In the end, you have to admit,
it all works out quite nicely.

733
01:11:07,080 --> 01:11:10,320
Don Kim gets his bullet, thanks to you,

734
01:11:10,480 --> 01:11:13,800
and Hong Kong gets a goat to take the fall.

735
01:11:14,480 --> 01:11:19,160
- Please understand, it's nothing personal.
- Speak for yourself.

736
01:11:22,440 --> 01:11:23,840
That what I think it is?

737
01:11:26,120 --> 01:11:28,280
It's the Chinese shit.

738
01:11:28,800 --> 01:11:31,200
Hold him down.

739
01:11:32,680 --> 01:11:35,720
Not so fast, motherfucker!

740
01:11:36,880 --> 01:11:39,040
He's gone dipsy-do, yo!

741
01:11:41,440 --> 01:11:43,040
Whatever, psycho.

742
01:11:45,680 --> 01:11:49,240
I'm afraid the Houdini act is over,
my friend.

743
01:11:56,760 --> 01:11:58,920
- Our Father, who art in...
- Shut up!

744
01:11:59,080 --> 01:12:02,000
So, this is how it is.

745
01:12:03,800 --> 01:12:07,600
- It's Don Kim! He's supposed to be dead!
- Presto.

746
01:12:29,520 --> 01:12:32,560
Police have moved
to surround the Hotel Lint,

747
01:12:32,760 --> 01:12:35,280
where the madman
behind today's mayhem...

748
01:12:35,640 --> 01:12:39,120
is holed up
and making a desperate last stand.

749
01:12:39,280 --> 01:12:42,000
Officials have confirmed
gunfire on the sundeck.

750
01:12:42,160 --> 01:12:47,040
Our news chopper will bring live,
uncensored coverage from above the hotel.

751
01:12:47,200 --> 01:12:54,000
Again, this coverage is uncensored, so any
small children present should leave the room.

752
01:13:06,320 --> 01:13:07,560
Get me out of here!

753
01:13:16,080 --> 01:13:17,440
I'll kill you, Chelios!

754
01:13:18,120 --> 01:13:19,240
Too late!

755
01:13:25,200 --> 01:13:26,440
Look out!

756
01:13:27,600 --> 01:13:28,800
Thanks, boss.

757
01:14:46,160 --> 01:14:49,240
Let's get the fuck out of here, now!
Let's go!

758
01:14:55,480 --> 01:14:56,760
Present from Kaylo.

759
01:15:05,080 --> 01:15:07,040
Now what?
Now you say shit!

760
01:15:07,240 --> 01:15:08,560
Where the fuck were you?

761
01:15:09,760 --> 01:15:11,160
Who's the bitch, now?

762
01:15:18,200 --> 01:15:20,280
No, no! You fly, motherfucker!

763
01:15:21,880 --> 01:15:23,440
Motherfuckin' fly!

764
01:16:11,160 --> 01:16:12,160
You're dead!

765
01:16:13,560 --> 01:16:17,760
Oh my God!

766
01:16:27,760 --> 01:16:30,200
You're dead! You're dead, motherfucker!

767
01:16:58,800 --> 01:17:01,880
I told you I'd kill you, you little bitch!

768
01:17:23,680 --> 01:17:26,800
Hey, its Eve.
I'm glad you called but I'm not here.

769
01:17:27,040 --> 01:17:31,280
Leave a message, unless you're
selling something 'cause I'm not interested.

770
01:17:31,440 --> 01:17:34,920
If you're not, then just...
Wait, time's up.

771
01:17:35,800 --> 01:17:37,440
Hey, doll...

772
01:17:39,160 --> 01:17:42,560
Looks like I let you down, again.

773
01:17:43,160 --> 01:17:47,840
Seems like all my life
I've just been going... going...

774
01:17:48,480 --> 01:17:49,880
going...

775
01:17:50,040 --> 01:17:54,440
I wish I'd taken more time to
stop and smell the roses, so to speak.

776
01:17:56,720 --> 01:18:00,560
Well, I guess it's too late for that now.

777
01:18:04,400 --> 01:18:09,000
You're the greatest, baby.

778
01:18:09,001 --> 01:19:10,001
Subtitled By DeliXiosO
